    Interface Description
    AgentList
    AgentList interface manages a list of agents.
    Condition
    Condition interface represents an ungrounded condition.
    Congestion
    Congestion interface provides methods to deal with congestion operators.
    CongestionFluent
    CongestionFluent interface provides methods to deal with congestion fluents.
    CongestionPenalty
    CongestionPenalty interface provides methods to deal with congestion penalties.
    CongestionUsage
    CongestionUsage interface provides methods to deal with the usage section in the congestion operators.
    Fact
    Fact interface provides methods to deal with ungrounded facts.
    Function
    Fact interface provides methods to deal with ungrounded functions.
    Metric
    Metric interface provides methods to deal with metric functions.
    NumericEffect
    NumericEffect interface provides methods to deal with action numeric effects.
    NumericExpression
    NumericExpression interface provides methods to deal with numeric expressions.
    NumericFact
    NumericExpression interface provides methods to deal with numeric facts (function(param1,param2,...) = value).
    Operator
    Operator interface provides methods to deal with operators (ungrounded actions).
    Parameter
    Parameter interface represents a parameter, i.e. a name with a list of types.
